<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>我的电子书小铺</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; background: #f0f2f5; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; padding: 24px 16px; }
        .container { max-width: 880px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; border-radius: 32px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 20px 35px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 48px 32px; text-align: center; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .section { padding: 40px 32px; }
        .section h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 24px; color: #333; border-bottom: 3px solid #667eea; display: inline-block; }
        .book { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px; padding: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px; background: #f8f9ff; border-radius: 16px; }
        .book-icon { font-size: 3rem; background: white; width: 80px; height: 80px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border-radius: 16px; }
        .price { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: bold; color: #764ba2; }
        .buy-btn { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 28px; border-radius: 25px; font-size: 1rem; cursor: pointer; }
        .faq { margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 16px; background: #f8f9ff; border-radius: 12px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 24px; color: #999; font-size: 0.9rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
        .modal { display: none; position: fixed; z-index: 1000; left: 0; top: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5); align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
        .modal-content { background: white; padding: 32px; border-radius: 20px; text-align: center; max-width: 360px; width: 90%; }
        .modal-content img { width: 200px; height: 200px; object-fit: contain; margin: 16px 0; border-radius: 12px; }
        .close-btn { background: #ddd; border: none; padding: 8px 24px; border-radius: 20px; cursor: pointer; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>📚 我的电子书小铺</h1>
            <p>精选优质内容 · 即买即看</p >
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <h2>热卖电子书</h2>
            <div class="book">
                <div class="book-icon">📅</div>
                <div>
                    <h3>7天居家效率手册</h3>
                    <p>提高居家办公/学习效率的实用指南</p >
                    <div class="price">¥9.90</div>
                    <button class="buy-btn" onclick="openQR()">立即购买</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="book">
                <div class="book-icon">🏠</div>
                <div>
                    <h3>天天家装分享</h3>
                    <p>装修避坑指南 + 风格灵感合集</p >
                    <div class="price">¥9.90</div>
                    <button class="buy-btn" onclick="openQR()">立即购买</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <h2>常见问题</h2>
            <div class="faq"><strong>Q：这本书适合什么样的人？</strong><br>A：适合经常在家办公或学习容易被分心的人</div>
            <div class="faq"><strong>Q：购买后如何收到电子书？</strong><br>A：支付后发PDF到您的邮箱</div>
            <div class="faq"><strong>Q：可以退款吗？</strong><br>A：30天内可全额退款</div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">© 2026 我的电子书小铺 · Powered by GitHub Pages</div>
    </div>
    <div id="qrModal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <h3>扫码支付 ¥9.90</h3>
            <p style="color:#666;">支持支付宝 / 微信 / 云闪付</p >
            < img src="mmexport1711982891801.jpg" alt="收款二维码" id="qrcodeImg">
            <p style="color:#999; font-size:12px;">支付后截图发邮箱，5分钟内发PDF</p >
            <button class="close-btn" onclick="closeQR()">关闭</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script>
        function openQR() { document.getElementById('qrModal').style.display = 'flex'; }
        function closeQR() { document.getElementById('qrModal').style.display = 'none'; }
        window.onclick = function(event) { var m = document.getElementById('qrModal'); if (event.target === m) m.style.display = 'none'; }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
